---
import ThemeLayout from '../layouts/ThemeLayout.astro';
---
<ThemeLayout page="services" heading="Professional Website Development">

  <section class="inner-page padd-section">
    <div class="container">

      <div class="row align-items-center mb-5" data-aos="fade-up">
        <div class="col-md-2 col-sm-12 text-center mb-4 mb-md-0">
          <div class="svc-hero-icon">
            <i class="fa fa-desktop"></i>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-10">
          <h3>Complete Frontend &amp; Backend Web Development</h3>
          <p>Rayinfos Technologies delivers a complete range of frontend and backend services compliant with the latest industry trends — from simple brochure sites to complex web portals. Every project is supervised by a dedicated project manager, with Agile-influenced methodology and a strict QA process at every stage.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="row" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
          <div class="svc-card">
            <div class="svc-card-icon"><i class="fa fa-eye"></i></div>
            <h5>Stylish Design</h5>
            <p>Appealing, unique web designs using the latest tools — stylish professional layouts, compatible colours and consistent corporate identity.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
          <div class="svc-card">
            <div class="svc-card-icon"><i class="fa fa-sitemap"></i></div>
            <h5>User-friendly Navigation</h5>
            <p>Simple, intuitive navigation tools with accessible options and a clear, easy-to-manoeuvre layout that keeps visitors engaged.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
          <div class="svc-card">
            <div class="svc-card-icon"><i class="fa fa-code"></i></div>
            <h5>Front-end Development</h5>
            <p>Interactive and functional front-end development compatible with the latest technologies, including database design and page generation.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
          <div class="svc-card">
            <div class="svc-card-icon"><i class="fa fa-cog"></i></div>
            <h5>Back-office Administration</h5>
            <p>Integrated back-office management tools for content publishing, structure generation, document management and site statistics.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
          <div class="svc-card">
            <div class="svc-card-icon"><i class="fa fa-comments"></i></div>
            <h5>Agile Process</h5>
            <p>Development methodology influenced by Agile and RUP, with a dedicated project manager and two-way communication throughout.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
          <div class="svc-card">
            <div class="svc-card-icon"><i class="fa fa-check-circle"></i></div>
            <h5>Quality Assurance</h5>
            <p>Dedicated QA personnel monitoring every stage: HTML compliance, GUI testing, performance, stability and accurate coding standards.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

</ThemeLayout>
